<s> Personal response: I think you would stand a better chance of getting this proposal through the working group if (a) you stated a justification as to why you think this change is beneficial (don't assume that the benefits are obvious) (b) you made a proposal as to how the language should deal with the resulting "dangling else" ambiguity.  </s>
<s> (For my own part, I would have much prefered a syntax in which expressions were self-closing, e.g. if (Expr) then Expr [else Expr] fi But I lost that battle.  </s>
<s> I don't think it would be a good idea to make "else" optional unless we introduce a mandatory closer to remove the ambiguity.)  </s>
<s> Michael Kay  </s>
